1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,389
Hello everyone, I'm making this video
to promote the candidacy of

2
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:06,589
Jérôme Lepagnol for the position
representative director

3
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,589
of SG employee shareholders
Who am I in 2 dates?

4
00:00:11,600 --> 00:00:16,089
1993 : at 24 years old, I created my company
at the end of my studies, I develop it

5
00:00:16,100 --> 00:00:18,799
for 12 years to resell it
with a very nice margin.

6
00:00:19,400 --> 00:00:24,188
2016 : at 47 years old, I become an executive
and I participate to the Board of Directors.

7
00:00:24,200 --> 00:00:26,388
of a French SME with
an international scope

8
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:27,788
and more than 1000 people

9
00:00:27,800 --> 00:00:32,389
Now let's talk about Jerome,
who I have known for more than 25 years.

10
00:00:32,400 --> 00:00:37,989
What I like most about him,
are his qualities of <i>savoir-être</i>

11
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:41,089
and his ability to adapt.

12
00:00:41,100 --> 00:00:43,889
Jérôme knows how to listen, to bring a
new vision, without judging,

13
00:00:43,900 --> 00:00:46,789
how to defend opinions
with tact and intelligence

14
00:00:46,800 --> 00:00:49,989
and his curiosity to
better understand others

15
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:53,689
often brings a new perspective,
fruitfull for all.

16
00:00:53,700 --> 00:00:59,289
Moreover and beyond that, his
human qualities of integrity,

17
00:00:59,300 --> 00:01:05,088
seriousness, honesty and
search for justice

18
00:01:05,099 --> 00:01:06,799
make him a "good" man.

19
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:11,389
Reading his manifesto,
two sections

20
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:17,088
particularly raised my attention :
the first section when he says

21
00:01:17,100 --> 00:01:21,088
"We fully support SG’s purpose:

22
00:01:21,100 --> 00:01:25,389
Building together,
with our clients

23
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:27,189
a better and sustainable
future through responsible

24
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:30,999
and innovative financial solutions.”
This is an idea that echoes

25
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:33,989
an entrepreneur at heart
like me who considers the bank

26
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:36,989
has become an
institution that only lends to

27
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:40,399
the extent of the amounts
it can recover immediately.

28
00:01:41,500 --> 00:01:45,689
The second section, when he says
"Reconcile strategic decisions

29
00:01:45,700 --> 00:01:49,489
towards work compensation
and capital income

30
00:01:49,500 --> 00:01:52,588
both of them is necessary to the other :
let’s make them work in symbiosis

31
00:01:52,600 --> 00:01:57,189
no need for opposition.": this motivation
speaks to me especially given the news

32
00:01:57,200 --> 00:02:01,389
of the recent months
showing unions defending

33
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:04,899
their "private preserve" while
forgetting the very essence

34
00:02:04,900 --> 00:02:07,499
of their existence:
the defense of employees.

35
00:02:07,500 --> 00:02:10,989
In fact, I find this
manifesto modern

36
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:13,289
and committed to the human
under all its forms,

37
00:02:13,300 --> 00:02:16,089
representing values
of innovation,

38
00:02:16,100 --> 00:02:19,589
of responsibility and of commitment
which are those of Société Générale.

39
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:23,289
It is for these reasons
that if I had to vote

40
00:02:23,300 --> 00:02:26,699
to choose the administrator
representing me as

41
00:02:26,700 --> 00:02:30,189
employee shareholder,
I would choose Jérôme because

42
00:02:30,200 --> 00:02:35,099
Voting Jérôme means voting for you
I wish you a good day.

43
00:02:35,600 --> 00:02:37,799
And above all take care for you.
